title: Update: Romeo Needs Help Making A Big Change Before This Major Event
description:
Romeo's anxiety is through the roof! IT's hard for him to truly be himself because he's always in his head stressing out about the things he can't control.
With a big event coming up, he knows it's time to seek some mental help beforehand.
